title: Answering "White Privilege" (Vs. Joey Carbstrong!)
description: Vegans should be prepared to deal with questions of how our claims clash with traditional, indigenous culture —with or without the language of "privilege".  We need to be prepared for this type of rhetoric because Veganism is a challenge to every cultural tradition: indigenous or not, white or not, privileged or not.  Here's how I address it —in contrast to Joey Carbstrong.
